Data Structures
Here are the data structures with brief descriptions:
 CI2c_DevInitParamsI2C Device Initialization Object
 Clld_hsi2c_datatfr_params_sLld_hsi2c_datatfr_params_s contains the I2C transfer parameters. This is passed as an argument to lld_i2c_transfer() API
 Clld_hsi2c_initParam_sLld_hsi2c_initParam_s contains the I2C initialisation parameters. This is passed as an argument to lld_i2c_init() API. see lld_hsi2c_opMode
 Clld_hsi2c_transreceive_params_sLld_hsi2c_transreceive_params_t contains the transfer parameters. This is passed as an argument to lld_i2c_transReceive() API
